title: Dungeons Of Eternity VR - Gauntlet Style Co-Op Greatness!
description:
I give you an early look at Dungeons Of Eternity on Quest 2. In this co-op gameplay video I jump into Dungeons Of Eternity with Gamertag VR and Beardo Benjo. This co-op dungeon crawler is coming to Quest 2, Quest Pro and Quest 3 soon!

Check out Dungeons Of Eternity on Quest here;
https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/6341779295861881

Join the Dungeons Of Eternity Discord here;
https://discord.com/invite/BGUKmRCW3V

Enter the giveaway to win a Quest 3 here;
https://gleam.io/competitions/k3HLu-dungeons-of-eternity-quest-3-contest

Thanks to Othergate for sponsoring this gameplay video with a paid promotion and for hosting the giveaway.

Let me know what you think of Dungeons Of Eternity on Quest in the comments below...

Thanks for watching []-)
